subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Denny Hamlin won the Chevy Rock & Roll 400, but his teammate Kyle Busch did not qualify for the 12-driver Chase for the Sprint Cup.
